cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this library in your work, please cite using the metadata below."
type: software
title: "confidence-escalation: Confidence-Gated Escalation Middleware for LLM Agents"
abstract: >
  Framework-agnostic middleware implementing confidence-gated escalation for LLM
  agents. Combines logprob, verbalized confidence, and tool-call risk signals into
  threshold-based escalation policies with pluggable handlers for human review,
  model upgrade, and compliance logging. Addresses OWASP Agentic AI ASI-09 and
  EU AI Act Article 14 human oversight requirements.
authors:
